description: This course helps students prepare for the 11+ Entrance exams. With a mixture of video tuition and PDF resources, it will develop your understanding of what examiners are looking for in each paper; Maths, English and Verbal Reasoning. The course has been divided into sections, and once you have completed the video lectures for each course, you are given a number of additional practice papers and worksheets designed to test your skills and understanding. Collectively, the materials we have provided for you, as well as a sufficient amount of time spent practising, will enable you to achieve a grade high enough to ensure entry to the UK's best schools.
title: 11+ Exam Preparation / UK Grammar and Private Schools
